Q100. (High-Level CDS Multi-Statement)

Consider the following statements regarding the Directive Principles of State Policy (DPSPs):

They are contained in Part IV of the Constitution.
They are enforceable by courts.
They are fundamental in the governance of the country.

A) 1 and 2 only

B) 2 and 3 only

C) 1 and 3 only

D) 1, 2 and 3

